{"tid":1980364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：華倘故意瞞疫須面對後果","createTime":"2020-04-20T05:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T05:30:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"37888af622519420f0818f46039e0d06b3d68e45","tid":1980364,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:02:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200420/TQAJAOTGFDPIYZGOJGAKBHRRFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FTQAJAOTGFDPIYZGOJGAKBHRRFY%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=a59bf5bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FTQAJAOTGFDPIYZGOJGAKBHRRFY%2F&h=8e41dab7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200420/TQAJAOTGFDPIYZGOJGAKBHRRFY/</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普：華倘故意瞞疫須面對後果<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】現時全球多國正醞釀追究中國隱瞞疫情，中國掀起新外交風波。美國總統特朗普警告，如果證實中國蓄意隱瞞疫情，造成武漢肺炎全球大流行，中國須面對後果，但他沒說明會有甚麼後續行動。<br />\n<br />\n美國霍士新聞日前報道，武漢肺炎病毒很大可能是源於武漢的實驗室。特朗普其後表示，會查出病毒是否來自武漢的實驗室。特朗普在昨天疫情記者會說，疫情本可遏止於中國境內，但最終導致全球流行，質問「是過失導致失控，還是故意為之」。特朗普表示：「過失就是過失，如果那是他們故意，就肯定要承擔後果。」<br />\n<br />\n澳洲亦揚言要調查中國，澳洲外長潘恩（Marise Payne）指，澳洲發起對疫情的獨立調查，調查對象包括世衞和中國。她說：「我們需要獨立調查才能得知的細節，並藉此判別病毒起源，以及如何對付，還有資訊是否足夠透明與外界分享。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200420/large/1587311107_9b6a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200420%2Flarge%2F1587311107_9b6a.gif&h=fe0dbf15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白宮負責統籌抗疫工作的伯克斯發表報告，特朗普直言中國確診及死亡數字不可信。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳外長質疑北京透明度<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：28日潛伏期重計 限聚令勢延長<br />\n<br />\n潘恩不諱言，這場疫情讓澳洲和中國的關係有所改變，她最質疑的是北京的透明度。德國第一大報「畫報」（Bild）亦批評習近平，指中共除未承擔武漢肺炎責任，還大規模侵犯人權。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》引述消息指，英國斥資2,000萬美元（約1.5億港元）向兩間中國公司購買200萬套武漢肺炎抗體檢測工具，後來被揭檢測工具無效。中國公司更要求先付款，要英方自行從中國廠房取貨，英政府正着手追收退款。但中國廠商辯稱，是英方誤解或誇大檢測工具效用，又稱工具不適用於早期篩查及確診。"},{"pid":"fc215074533e93b4245ee4f79958b5de26d46bea","tid":1980364,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:04:33.000Z","msg":"百國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nthis way sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家想比邊個國家殖民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d63d710688fa31ca4b60a0997610fe648a4e45","tid":1980364,"uid":133828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:05:36.000Z","msg":"又話係good friend<br />\n<br />\n突然咁多呢d news<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32380df91aeabba35a276737cdbb41603c67b8df","tid":1980364,"uid":182222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9d63d710688fa31ca4b60a0997610fe648a4e45","tid":1980364,"uid":133828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:05:36.000Z","msg":"又話係good friend<br />\n<br />\n突然咁多呢d news<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"要連任呀嘛<br />\n連任到先繼續做到good friend <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7560158d45f065363597bd15e8025d0129a186","tid":1980364,"uid":182222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc215074533e93b4245ee4f79958b5de26d46bea","tid":1980364,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:04:33.000Z","msg":"百國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nthis way sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家想比邊個國家殖民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"自己地頭自己話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e8e19014b13d4629cdc6d35c8cf4aeb6a